    question: "Can clients book grooming appointments online?",
    answer: "Yes. Good grooming software includes an online booking portal where clients can view real-time availability, select their preferred groomer, choose services (bath, full groom, nail trim, etc.), see pricing by breed size, and book 24/7 without calling. Clients receive instant confirmation and automated reminders before their appointment."
  },
  {
    question: "Will grooming software reduce no-shows?",
    answer: "Yes. Grooming salons using automated SMS and email reminders typically reduce no-shows by 70%. Advanced features like deposit collection (capturing £10-20 at booking time), prepayment options, and easy rescheduling further protect revenue. Some salons also implement cancellation fees for late cancellations, automatically managed by the software.",
    links: [
      { text: 'Dog Boarding Software', url: '/dog-boarding-software/' }
    ]
  },
  {
    question: "Does it track pet grooming history?",
    answer: "Yes. Pet grooming software stores complete grooming history including dates, services performed, groomer notes, clip styles, blade numbers, coat condition, temperament, and before/after photos. Every groomer sees the full history before each appointment, ensuring consistent results. Owners can also view their pet's grooming history through the owner portal."
  },
  {
    question: "Can it handle different pricing by breed?",
    answer: "Yes. Configure services with different pricing based on breed size (small, medium, large, giant), coat type (short, long, curly, double-coat), and service complexity. For example, a Labrador full groom might be £45 while a Standard Poodle is £75. The system shows correct pricing during online booking and automatically applies the right price at checkout."
  },
  {
    question: "Is there software for mobile groomers?",
    answer: "Yes. PetCare.Software includes mobile grooming features: route optimization (group appointments by area), automatic travel time buffers between appointments, service area management (only accept bookings within your coverage zone), mobile-first interface (full functionality from phone/tablet), offline mode for areas without signal, and GPS directions to appointments.",
    links: [
      { text: 'Kennel Software', url: '/kennel-software/' }
    ]
  },
  {
    question: "Does it integrate with payment processing?",
    answer: "Yes. Grooming software integrates with payment processors like Stripe for card payments. Process transactions, issue refunds, manage deposits, track retail product sales, apply discounts, and handle gift cards—all from one system. Integrated payments eliminate double-entry and automatically reconcile your accounts."
  },
  {
    question: "Can I manage multiple groomers?",
    answer: "Yes. Manage multiple groomers with individual calendars, availability schedules, service specializations, and performance tracking. Clients can select their preferred groomer during online booking. The system balances workload, prevents overbooking, tracks individual revenue and appointment counts, and manages staff holidays and days off.",
    links: [
      { text: 'Dog Daycare Software', url: '/dog-daycare-software/' }
    ]
  }
];
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Pet Grooming Software Guide (2026) - Online Booking & Salon Management"
  description="Pet grooming software that cuts admin time by 50%. Online booking, automated reminders, detailed pet profiles, and POS for grooming salons and mobile groomers."
  image="/images/hero-pets.jpg"
>
  <!-- Breadcrumbs with Schema -->
  <div class="bg-gray-100 py-3">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <BreadcrumbsEnhanced items={breadcrumbs} site="petcare" />
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-navy to-gray-900 text-white py-16">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
      <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background-image: url('/images/hero-grooming.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container-custom relative">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <span class="inline-block bg-brand-red/20 text-brand-red-light px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm mb-4">Complete Guide</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Pet Grooming Software</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-4">
          <strong>Pet grooming software</strong> cuts your admin time in half. Stop juggling phone calls, paper diaries, and manual reminders. Automate bookings, reduce no-shows, and focus on what you do best—making pets look amazing.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8">Last updated: January 2026 | Reading time: 10 minutes</p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="/contact/" class="btn-primary text-lg px-8 py-4">Start Free Trial</a>
          <a href="#what-is" class="btn-secondary text-lg px-8 py-4">Read the Guide</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Featured Answer for Featured Snippet -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <FeaturedAnswer question="What is pet grooming software?">
          Pet grooming software is a specialized management platform for grooming salons and mobile groomers that handles appointment scheduling, online booking, automated reminders, detailed pet profiles with grooming history, point of sale, payment processing, and business reporting. Modern platforms save salons 15+ hours weekly while reducing no-shows by 70% through automated reminders.
        </FeaturedAnswer>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Statistics Section with Dataset Schema -->
  <section class="section bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <StatisticsSection
          title="UK Pet Grooming Industry Statistics 2026"
          description="Key metrics showing growth and digital transformation in pet grooming"
          stats={groomingStats}
          layout="grid"
          source="UK Pet Grooming Industry Report 2026 & PFMA Data"
          datePublished="2026-01-01"
          site="petcare"
          pageUrl={Astro.url.href}
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Table of Contents -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">In This Guide</h2>
          <ul class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-gray-700">
            <li><a href="#what-is" class="hover:text-brand-red">→ What Is Grooming Software?</a></li>
            <li><a href="#features" class="hover:text-brand-red">→ Must-Have Features</a></li>
            <li><a href="#comparison" class="hover:text-brand-red">→ Software Comparison</a></li>
            <li><a href="#benefits" class="hover:text-brand-red">→ Benefits for Your Business</a></li>
            <li><a href="#mobile" class="hover:text-brand-red">→ Mobile Grooming Solutions</a></li>
            <li><a href="#faq" class="hover:text-brand-red">→ FAQ</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">

        <h2 id="what-is" class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">What Is Pet Grooming Software?</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          <strong>Pet grooming software</strong> is a comprehensive management system designed specifically for grooming salons and mobile pet groomers. It handles everything from appointment scheduling and client management to point of sale and business analytics—replacing paper diaries, spreadsheets, and manual reminder calls.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
          The best grooming software includes online booking portals, automated reminders, detailed pet profiles (coat type, temperament, special needs), grooming history, and integrated payment processing. At PetCare.Software, we also support mixed facilities—so if you offer <a href="/dog-daycare-software/" class="text-brand-red hover:underline">daycare</a>, <a href="/dog-boarding-software/" class="text-brand-red hover:underline">boarding</a>, or other services alongside grooming, everything stays in one system.
        </p>

        <h2 id="features" class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-12 mb-6">Must-Have Features for Grooming Software</h2>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Online Appointment Booking</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Let clients book 24/7 through your website. They see real availability, choose their groomer, select services, and confirm—no phone calls needed.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Automated Reminders</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">SMS and email reminders sent automatically before appointments. Dramatically reduces no-shows and last-minute cancellations.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Detailed Pet Profiles</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Store coat type, breed, temperament notes, health conditions, preferred styles, and photos. Every groomer sees the full history before each appointment.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Service & Pricing Management</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Configure services by breed size, coat type, and complexity. Set prices, durations, and available add-ons like teeth cleaning or nail painting.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Point of Sale & Payments</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Process card payments, track retail sales, apply discounts, and manage gift cards. Integrated payments mean no double-entry.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Client Communication</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Send booking confirmations, reminders, follow-ups, and marketing messages. Keep clients informed without manual effort.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-8 mb-4">Advanced Features</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 mb-8">
          <li><strong>Before/after photos:</strong> Document your work and share with delighted owners</li>
          <li><strong>Grooming notes:</strong> Track clip styles, blade numbers, and preferences for consistency</li>
          <li><strong>Vaccination tracking:</strong> Block appointments for pets with expired vaccines</li>
          <li><strong>Staff scheduling:</strong> Manage groomer availability, holidays, and workload</li>
          <li><strong>Recurring appointments:</strong> Set up repeat bookings for regular clients</li>
          <li><strong>Waitlist management:</strong> Fill cancellations quickly from a ready waitlist</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 id="comparison" class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-12 mb-6">How Grooming Software Compares</h2>
        <ComparisonTable
          title="Pet Grooming Software Feature Comparison"
          description="Compare PetCare.Software against generic booking tools and manual management"
          headers={['Feature', 'PetCare.Software', 'Generic Booking Tools', 'Paper Diary']}
          rows={comparisonData}
          sortable={true}
        />

        <h2 id="benefits" class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-12 mb-6">Benefits for Your Grooming Business</h2>

        <div class="bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-brand-red p-4 my-6 rounded">
          <p class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">The numbers don't lie</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Grooming salons using dedicated software report <strong>50% less time on admin</strong>, <strong>70% fewer no-shows</strong>, and <strong>20% more appointments per week</strong> through better scheduling efficiency.</p>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-8 mb-4">For Salon Owners</h3>
        <div class="space-y-4 mb-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-brand-red text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">✓</div>
            <div>
              <strong class="text-brand-navy">Reclaim your evenings:</strong>
              <span class="text-gray-700"> Stop returning calls and confirming appointments after hours</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-brand-red text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">✓</div>
            <div>
              <strong class="text-brand-navy">Reduce revenue leakage:</strong>
              <span class="text-gray-700"> Deposits and reminders protect against no-shows</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-brand-red text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">✓</div>
            <div>
              <strong class="text-brand-navy">Make data-driven decisions:</strong>
              <span class="text-gray-700"> See which services are most profitable, which days are busiest</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-brand-red text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">✓</div>
            <div>
              <strong class="text-brand-navy">Scale without chaos:</strong>
              <span class="text-gray-700"> Add groomers without your admin workload multiplying</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-brand-red text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">✓</div>
            <div>
              <strong class="text-brand-navy">Professional image:</strong>
              <span class="text-gray-700"> Online booking and automated communications impress clients</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-8 mb-4">For Groomers</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
          <li><strong>Know what's coming:</strong> See full pet profiles before each appointment</li>
          <li><strong>Consistent results:</strong> Access grooming notes and previous styles</li>
          <li><strong>Less interruption:</strong> Clients book online instead of calling during grooms</li>
          <li><strong>Fair workload:</strong> Automated scheduling balances appointments across staff</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 id="mobile" class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-12 mb-6">Mobile Grooming Software</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Mobile groomers have unique needs. You're managing a business from a van, often with limited connectivity, while also handling driving routes and travel time between appointments.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-8 mb-4">Key Features for Mobile Groomers</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
          <li><strong>Route optimization:</strong> Group appointments by area to minimize driving</li>
          <li><strong>Travel time buffers:</strong> Automatically add travel time between appointments</li>
          <li><strong>Service area management:</strong> Only accept bookings within your coverage zone</li>
          <li><strong>Mobile-first interface:</strong> Full functionality from your phone or tablet</li>
          <li><strong>Offline mode:</strong> Continue working even without signal</li>
          <li><strong>GPS directions:</strong> Navigate to appointments with integrated maps</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
          Mobile grooming is one of the fastest-growing segments of the pet industry. The right software helps you serve more clients efficiently while maintaining the personalized service that sets mobile groomers apart.
        </p>

        <p>Related: <a href="/dog-daycare-software/" class="text-brand-red hover:underline">Dog Daycare Software</a> | <a href="/dog-boarding-software/" class="text-brand-red hover:underline">Dog Boarding Software</a> | <a href="/kennel-software/" class="text-brand-red hover:underline">Kennel Software</a></p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section with Enhanced Component -->
  <section class="section bg-gray-50" id="faq">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <FAQEnhanced
          faqs={faqItems}
          title="Frequently Asked Questions"
          searchable={true}
          site="petcare"
          pageUrl={Astro.url.href}
          initiallyExpanded={0}
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="section bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-red to-red-700 text-white">
    <div class="container-custom text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to Upgrade Your Grooming Salon?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-90">Join hundreds of groomers who've ditched the paper diary. See how PetCare.Software handles bookings, reminders, and payments—all in one place.</p>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn bg-white text-brand-red hover:bg-gray-100 text-lg px-8 py-4">Start Free 14-Day Trial</a>
      <p class="text-sm mt-4 opacity-75">No credit card required. Set up in 15 minutes.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Related Content -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-8 text-center">Related Guides</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <a href="/dog-daycare-software/" class="card p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Dog Daycare Software</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Playgroup management and daily care</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/dog-boarding-software/" class="card p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Dog Boarding Software</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Overnight stays and extended boarding</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/kennel-software/" class="card p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Kennel Software</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Complete kennel management</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
